{"tid":1920362,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[牙膏16春] Intel 次世代 Alder Lake-S LGA 1700 處理器曝光","createTime":"2020-03-11T11:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T03:26:46.000Z","uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"880f04532a6e640744ce6ee1d5053a667afff905","tid":1920362,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2020/03/320x240/09170803831879459079.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2020%2F03%2F320x240%2F09170803831879459079.jpg&h=7a5ce605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據此前的爆料，Intel 將會明顯加快在 2020 年後對桌面處理器的推動速度快，追回之前已落後的時間，目前第十代 Core 處理器 Comet Lake-S 即將上市，而在它後面還有 14nm 的 Rocket Lake-S，之後真正的 10nm 桌面處理器 Alder Lake-S 就會接手，之前已有傳聞指 Alder Lake-S 將會用上長方形設計及更換上 LGA1700 針腳，最新再有爆料稱 Alder Lake-S 或會採用類似於 <strong>Arm 的 big.LITTLE 大小核設計，由 8 個大核心及 8 個小核心組合而成，TDP 最高 150W，更會支援 PCI-Express 4.0 傳輸。</strong><br />\n <br />\n目前，Intel 正準備發佈基於<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 14nm </span></span></strong>工藝的第十代 Comet Lake-S，Comet Lake-S 的旗艦產品最多會有 10 核心、20 線程，因為升級了核心數目接口及主機板都會換新，預計將採用全新的 LGA1200 及 400 系列主機板。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/09/source/03201519191195352985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F09%2Fsource%2F03201519191195352985.jpg&h=d4acbd33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://file1.hkepc.net/2019/01/source/0819592868816963970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffile1.hkepc.net%2F2019%2F01%2Fsource%2F0819592868816963970.jpg&h=da6594e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkepc.com/19090/%E8%86%A0%E6%B0%B4_16_%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83_%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98_150W%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4_PCIe_4.0_Intel_%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%96%E4%BB%A3_Alder_Lake-S_LGA_1700_%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkepc.